2. select 32 or 64 bit
3. double click setup.exe
4. now its on your hard drive so look for it. program files/adobe cs6 master collection
5. open this folder and double click MasterCollection_CS6_LS16, it should have a gray folder next to it.
6. hit next
7. while this is running, "preparing files", go back to the folder (Adobe Master Collection CS6 in your
program files) and open the Crack folder
8. then open the crack subfolder
9. double click cs6.patch
10. click Patch
10. it will ask you to locate the file, hit Yes
11. mine was here, C:Program FilesAdobe CS6 Master CollectionCrackamtlib.dll64-bit, or 32bit, 
whichever you selected in the beginning.

14. meanwhile, your "preparing files" process should be just about complete.

20. After its done installing, go to the folder you installed it into. mine was under program files/adobe

22. NOW, open each folder and start to paste the cracked files in them. For example, open Adobe After Effects CS6, then
Support Files, and PASTE! it will ask you if you want to replace existing files, YES, replace existing files!
23. Test your might! Start Adobe After Effects CS6 and it will bypass the trial screen prompt and open up normally.

before pasting the cracked files. I DID, AND BECAUSE I READ, PHOTOSHOP CS6 STARTED NORMALLY!
